      "replayEndSec": 8.575098,
      "narrationText": "Register the server from the command line. You give it a name, its IP address, and the SSH user. The name is just a local alias. We use machine-11 so it matches the IP, but it can be anything you like, such as prod-db or web-1. There is no separate init step; the config file is created automatically on first use.",
